title: Pinegrove Discography (duplicates removed)
description:
This torrent contains a folder for each album/EP release which include only the previously unreleased tracks on that release. There are multiple recordings of some songs, and those are included, but each version should only be included once.

ie, "Everything So Far" is basically a band-made discography, including everything in this torrent PLUS the two tracks which are in that folder. So instead of duplicating everything for that one release, I only included the two new tracks in that folder.

If you like the music, support the band!


Pinegrove is a five-piece band living in Brooklyn, NY. Members have variously called Montclair, NJ and Kenyon College home
